content.description: As crown jewel of their new Sender series, the Rossignol Sender 106 Ti Plus Skis carry the torch passed down from Rossi's previously iconic S-Series skis and trust us, they carry it well! With a unique combination of a poplar wood core, titanal metal, carbon alloy, and dampening laminates — not to mention Rossignol's signature AirTip tips/tails — the Sender 106 delivers a fusion of technical precision, high-octane stability, and all-mountain versatility. Whether you're presented with knee-deep pow, chopped up leftovers, steep trees, or fast, top-to-bottom groomers, you'll feel right at home on the Rossignol Sender 106 Ti Plus Skis.
content.name: Rossignol Sender 106 Ti Plus Skis 2023
